comment: West (IND) makes incidental contact with Nowitzki (DAL) that does not affect his RSBQ at the start of his move.
Parsons (DAL) makes contact with Hibbert's (IND) arm and the contact affects his layup attempt.
Harris (DAL) sets the screen on Mahinmi (IND), without giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
R-Slash shows Parsons (DAL) makes contact with Miles (IND) after the inbound, and then moves off to get the ball.
West (IND) creates space with Nowitzki (DAL), similar to Parsons on previous play.
Chandler (DAL) dislodges Hibbert (IND) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Miles (IND) obtains legal guarding position as he establishes himself in Parsons' (DAL) path and gives him enough room to stop and change directions.
RHH shows Hill (IND) legally defends Parsons' (DAL) jump shot. The "high five" contact after the ball is released is legal.
RHH shows Hill (IND) cuts off and pushes Harris (DAL) away from the rebounding area.
Nowitzki (DAL) commits a take foul on Miles (IND).
